OL,6,FWhile the focus today is rightly on
OL,7,Fthe lives changed by Monday's horrific
OL,8,Fscenes in Liverpool, there are also
OL,9,Fsigns that Merseyside Police is itself
OL,10,Ftransformed since the last time it
OL,11,Fdealt with an incident on this scale.
OL,13,FThree words indicate a step change in
OL,14,Fthe force's communications: "white
OL,15,FBritish man".
OL,17,FIt took them less than two hours to
OL,18,Finform us of the suspect's profile
OL,19,Flast night.
