OL,6,FContrast that with the vacuum of
OL,7,Finformation following the Southport
OL,8,Fmurders last July, and it's clear the
OL,9,Fpolice have learnt from the past.
OL,11,FI was in Southport a few hours after
OL,12,Fthree little girls - Elsie, Alice and
OL,13,FBebe - were killed and saw for myself
OL,14,Fhow disinformation filled the void
OL,15,Fleft by police communications.
OL,17,FOnline, outright lies spread about the
OL,18,Fattacker. Mainly that he was a Muslim
OL,19,Fasylum seeker who had arrived via a
OL,20,Fsmall boat. He wasn't and he hadn't.
