OL,6,FThis is something the inspectorate
OL,7,FHMICFRS subsequently criticised police
OL,8,Ffor, recently concluding that "the
OL,9,Fpolice service needs to better
OL,10,Fappreciate that fast-moving events
OL,11,Frequire it to respond with an accurate
OL,12,Fcounter-narrative".
OL,14,FSo this time, Merseyside Police acted
OL,15,Fquickly.
OL,17,FI noticed that within minutes last
OL,18,Fnight theories were once again
OL,19,Fcirculating on social media, where
OL,20,Firresponsible accounts deliberately
OL,21,Fstoked a particular narrative.
